  └─→ Design robust fix, validate against root cause and edge cases
  ↓
PHASE 7: Regression Test Generation
  └─→ Create tests for failure scenario and edge cases to prevent recurrence
  ↓
PHASE 8: Fix Implementation & Verification
  └─→ Apply fix, verify in isolated environment, confirm against root cause
  ↓
OUTPUT:
  ├─ Code Functionality Breakdown (what code actually does)
